      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver, though it shows its age in several areas. The exterior has visible paint fading on the hood and roof, along with some minor dings and scratches consistent with regular use. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining, and the air conditioning takes a few minutes to reach full cooling capacity. Mechanically, the car runs well, though it will likely need new brake pads and a suspension tune-up in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, functional car for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
