    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-cared for\u2014perfect for zipping around town or hitting the highway for a weekend getaway. It runs great and looks even better in person! I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
