      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and optimized by Double VANOS variable valve timing. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential for superior corner-exit traction. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including subframe reinforcement and rod bearing service, ensuring the structural integrity of the chassis. The suspension geometry remains true, offering precise turn-in and highly communicative steering feedback through the rack-and-pinion system. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, this is a mechanically robust example of the ultimate driving machine.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
