    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-cared-for car that balances performance with everyday reliability. The exterior paint retains a deep, glossy shine and has been regularly hand-washed and waxed; while you might find a few minor stone chips consistent with careful highway driving, the body is straight and free of any significant blemishes. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in. The leather seats are supple with minimal wear on the bolsters, and all interior electronics\u2014including the infotainment system, navigation, and climate control\u2014operate exactly as they should. Mechanically, this car is in great shape. It has a comprehensive service history showing oil changes and inspections performed at recommended intervals. The engine pulls strongly and idles smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the suspension remains tight and quiet over bumps. With plenty of life left on the tires and recent brake service, this car is ready to be driven home today without needing immediate investment.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
