      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014well-loved and ready for all your upcoming adventures! Everything runs smoothly, and it's super comfortable for those long weekend trips. I've taken great care of it, so you're getting a reliable car that still looks fantastic on the road. Come take it for a spin, I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I do!",
