    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit maintains excellent compression across all cylinders, delivering linear power through its six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double-VANOS system. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers crisp engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. Suspension geometry remains tight with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. While showing minor patina consistent with its mileage, the chassis remains a benchmark for analog driver engagement.",
